Invocation Name: driving noise
des: Lay down and imagine you're driving down the road wihout a care in the world. You'll be asleep in no time! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Driving Noise,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
